Interface EvictionManager<K,V>

All Known Implementing Classes:
EvictionManagerImpl
@ThreadSafe public interface EvictionManager<K,V>
Central component that deals with eviction of cache entries. This manager only controls notifications of when entries are evicted.
Since:
4.0
Author:
Manik Surtani
